	<purpose>
		<p>
     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
     representation of relationships between requirements which are
     expressed as relationships between requirement view definitions 
     that is the relationships are dependent on the version of the
     requirement and the view of that version.
   </p>
<p>
   The second edition of this part of ISO 10303 incorporated the modifications to the first edition listed below.
</p>
